---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<BaseLayout title="Roadmap - Building a Multi-Agent System" description="Our strategic battle plan to bridge the gap between data and a cure for ASPS. Systematically building a multi-agent system for oncology.">
    <div slot="head">
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" rel="preconnect"/>
        <link crossorigin="" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" rel="preconnect"/>
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
    </div>

  <!-- Fixed Background Layer -->
  <div class="fixed inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none bg-ref-bg-light dark:bg-ref-bg-dark transition-colors duration-300">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,#80808012_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,#80808012_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:24px_24px]"></div>
      <div class="absolute left-0 right-0 top-0 -z-10 m-auto h-[500px] w-[500px] rounded-full bg-purple-500/20 opacity-50 blur-[100px]"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Scrollable Content Layer -->
  <div class="relative z-10 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 font-sans">
    
    <!-- Header Section -->
    <header class="relative pt-6 pb-16 w-full">
        <div class="max-w-[90%] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight mb-6 leading-tight">
                <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-ref-primary to-indigo-600 dark:from-purple-400 dark:to-indigo-400">
                    Building a Multi-Agent System
                </span>
            </h1>
            <p class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                Our strategic battle plan to bridge the gap between data and a cure. Systematically building a multi-agent system capable of solving the logic of ASPS.
            </p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="max-w-[85%] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pb-24 space-y-16">
        
        <!-- Introduction -->
        <section class="text-center">
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                This is not merely a development schedule; it is our strategic battle plan to bridge the gap between data and a cure. We are systematically building a multi-agent system capable of solving the logic of ASPS.
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Phase 1: Semantic Ingestion -->
        <section class="mb-8">
            <div class="bg-ref-surface-light dark:bg-ref-surface-dark rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                    <div class="p-3 bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/50 rounded-lg text-green-600 flex-shrink-0">
                        <Icon name="mdi:database" class="w-6 h-6" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2"><span class="text-xs font-bold text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 uppercase tracking-wide">ðŸŸ¢ In Progress</span></div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Phase 1: Semantic Ingestion</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-4">Construct the high-fidelity Biomedical Knowledge Graph (BKG) specific to Sarcoma biology by deploying NLP agents to extract semantic triplets, mapping entities to ontologies, and integrating GraphRAG for multi-hop traversal.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Phase 2: Neuro-Symbolic Logic Engine -->
        <section class="mb-8">
            <div class="bg-ref-surface-light dark:bg-ref-surface-dark rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                    <div class="p-3 bg-yellow-100 dark:bg-yellow-900/50 rounded-lg text-yellow-600 flex-shrink-0">
                        <Icon name="mdi:brain" class="w-6 h-6" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2"><span class="text-xs font-bold text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-400 uppercase tracking-wide">ðŸŸ¡ Next Phase</span></div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Phase 2: Neuro-Symbolic Logic Engine</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-4">Enable the system to generate novel, biologically-consistent hypotheses using DeepProbLog, autonomous LLM agents, and explicit uncertainty quantification to reduce hallucinations.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Phase 3: In Silico Simulation & The Creator -->
        <section class="mb-8">
            <div class="bg-ref-surface-light dark:bg-ref-surface-dark rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                    <div class="p-3 bg-orange-100 dark:bg-orange-900/50 rounded-lg text-orange-600 flex-shrink-0">
                        <Icon name="mdi:microscope" class="w-6 h-6" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2"><span class="text-xs font-bold text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400 uppercase tracking-wide">ðŸŸ  Future</span></div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Phase 3: In Silico Simulation & "The Creator"</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-4">Filter candidates through structural validation (AlphaFold-Multimer), causal inference (digital twins, do-calculus), and automated creator agents to propose repurposing strategies.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Phase 4: Wet-Lab Validation Loop -->
        <section class="mb-8">
            <div class="bg-ref-surface-light dark:bg-ref-surface-dark rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                    <div class="p-3 bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/50 rounded-lg text-blue-600 flex-shrink-0">
                        <Icon name="mdi:test-tube" class="w-6 h-6" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2"><span class="text-xs font-bold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-wide">ðŸ”µ Future</span></div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Phase 4: The Wet-Lab Validation Loop</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-4">Convert digital results into executable experimental protocols, run partner lab validations, and feed outcomes back to the BKG for iterative model improvement and open collaboration.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

    </main>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
